# 2019-05-25

     The first version of Fuchsschwanz released today!

     This version comes with the following features:

          * user login, authentication & registration
          * set/delete personal information
          * away status
          * change nick
          * groups
            - public messages
            - moderation & booting
            - topics
            - visibility (visible, secret or invisible)
            - volume (quiet, normal or loud)
            - control (public, moderated, restricted or
	               controlled)
          * private messages
          * personal inbox
          * beep other users
          * query groups & users
          * message of the day
          * integrated help
